     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       cnsmrsm vs. mnmlsm
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       <a href="http://twitter.com/zen_habits">
        By L
       </a>
      </p>
      <p>
       Thr s n mst f s n ndrlyng dsr t by cl stff.
      </p>
      <p>
       It stms frm frs nd nscrts, I thnk, bt t s xpltd by crprtns nd dvrtsng. Advrtsng s dsgnd t gt s t dsr mr, t wnt t by, nd bcs t wrks s wll, w nd p byng wy, wy mr thn w nd.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mnmlsm s th xct cntr t ths phnmnn, nd fr sm f s, t’s th nswr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Thnk f trbl scts, nxpsd t cnsmrsm r dvrtsng. Thy dn’t hv rgs t g t nd by cl nw clths r gdgts r crs r shs. It’s nt tht thy dn’t hv dsrs, bt t’s nt t th sm scl s n r scty.
      </p>
      <p>
       Evn n th dys bfr dvrtsng, ths knds f dsrs fr mr wr nt s prvlnt. It s dvrtsng nd cnsmrsm tht hv crtd th dsrs, r t lst mgnfd thm t  hgly xggrtd lvl. It s xtrmly ffctv.
      </p>
      <p>
       Unfrtntly, t mns w r lwys wntng t by mr, nd lwys spndng mr. Whch mns w mst thr gt nt dbt, r wrk mr t rn mr. Or bth. And tdy, fmls mst hv tw wg rnrs — s ppsd t nly 50-60 yrs g, whn thr ws nly n wg rnr ncssry — n prt bcs w r tryng t spprt  mr xpnsv lfstyl (ls bcs w’r bng pd lss n rl dllrs). W’r ls mr n dbt thn vr bfr.
      </p>
      <p>
       W nd t stp nd sk rslvs — wht s t ll fr? Why r w wrkng s hrd n rdr t by s mch, t hv s mch, t b brdnd nd clttrd by s mch?
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s jst t mch. Mnmlsts sy, “I’m gttng ff ths mrry-g-rnd. I pt t.”
      </p>
      <p>
       Th mnmlst frst lks t nds vs. wnts — s ths  rl nd, r s t jst  dsr crtd by dvrtsng? And f t’s  wnt,  dsr, sh dsn’t by t.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th mnmlst slwly lrns t lt g f dsrs. It dsn’t hppn vrnght, bt t cn hppn, grdlly, wth  cnscs ffrt.
      </p>
      Hr’s hw I d t:
      <br/>
      <ul>
       <li>
        Lrn t b mr cnscs f my mplss whn I’m rdy t by smthng.
       </li>
       <li>
        Lrn t ps, nd t brth, t lt th physcl dsr wn.
       </li>
       <li>
        Frc myslf t wt, f th prchs sn’t n bslt ncssty.
       </li>
       <li>
        Lt myslf thnk bt t, nd nlyz whthr t’s smthng I rlly nd t by. Oftn th nswr s n.
       </li>
       <li>
        Slwly mprv pn ths, vr tm, s I lwys mk mstks.
       </li>
      </ul>
      Th mnmlst lts g f dsrs, slwly, s tht sh bys lss nd spnds lss, gts nt lss dbt (r nn t ll), nd s  rslt, nds t rn lss nd wrk lss.
      <p>
       <small>
       </small>
      </p>
